subject: Tennis
lead_paragraph: Top-ranked Jelena Jankovic defeated Flavia Pennetta, 7-6 (6), 6-3, and advanced to the semifinals of the Kremlin Cup in Moscow. Jankovic will face Elena Dementieva, who beat Nadia Petrova, 6-4, 4-6, 7-6 (6).
